00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:26,660
that are really good at inducing learning and plasticity, and the inhibitory parts haven't

236
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:28,180
come on yet.

237
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:32,820
So when we say that babies and young children are bad at paying attention, what we really

