00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:35,500
mean is that they're bad at not paying attention.

239
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:39,580
So they're bad at getting rid of all the interesting things that could tell them something and

240
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:41,940
just looking at the thing that's important.

241
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:46,900
That's the kind of attention, the kind of consciousness that we might expect from those

242
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:49,340
butterflies who are designed to learn.

243
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:53,780
Well, if we want to think about a way of getting a taste of that kind of baby consciousness

